WEBVTT

00:01.376 --> 00:03.933
That's a Windsor knot.
I had a 2-year-old.

00:03.933 --> 00:05.567
They took him and put
him in the foster system.

00:05.636 --> 00:06.835
What was his name?

00:06.904 --> 00:07.903
Ben.

00:07.971 --> 00:09.596
Gus, it worked. I got the mom.

00:09.768 --> 00:10.818
Dr. Kleiner: Just wanted to let you know

00:10.818 --> 00:12.641
that you missed your
hormone injection today.

00:12.710 --> 00:14.070
Once the drug's out of your system,

00:14.078 --> 00:15.078
the urges will resurface.

00:15.112 --> 00:16.552
- Where's Agent Clements?
- I don't know.

00:16.614 --> 00:17.493
- What did you do with him?
- I...

00:17.494 --> 00:19.014
What did you do with him?

00:19.083 --> 00:21.550
You have to make
them stop looking for you.

00:21.619 --> 00:22.784
Did you hurt my brother?!

00:22.853 --> 00:23.785
Yes.

00:23.854 --> 00:24.853
I'll give you the money back...

00:24.922 --> 00:26.154
the $10,000.

00:26.223 --> 00:28.423
Is that what my brother's life is worth?

00:28.492 --> 00:29.324
Is that him?

00:29.393 --> 00:30.158
No. It's not him.

00:30.227 --> 00:31.267
Let him take another look.

00:31.328 --> 00:32.895
We know that he's been wrong before.

00:32.963 --> 00:34.263
Why did he lie?

00:34.331 --> 00:36.598
The man who took your
son didn't kill Adam.

00:36.667 --> 00:38.467
Ben did.

00:38.535 --> 00:40.602
My mother is honored

00:40.671 --> 00:45.507
and she will give her
acceptance speech as soon as she's well.

00:45.576 --> 00:47.409
<i>Ben: Picture your life.</i>

00:50.614 --> 00:53.921
<i>A series of moments stacked
up like a house of cards.</i>

00:54.178 --> 00:56.314
_

00:56.553 --> 01:01.189
<i>If you could re-live any one of them,</i>

01:01.258 --> 01:02.791
<i>would you do it different?</i>

01:02.860 --> 01:04.893
Help! My name is Adam Warren!

01:04.962 --> 01:05.794
Help us!

01:05.863 --> 01:07.296
Want to play?

01:07.364 --> 01:08.797
My name is Adam Warren!

01:08.866 --> 01:09.665
Help us!

01:09.733 --> 01:10.999
Help me!

01:11.068 --> 01:13.402
I tried that. No one can hear us.

01:14.905 --> 01:16.838
Someone saw him take me.

01:16.907 --> 01:19.274
You can be red this time.

01:19.343 --> 01:22.377
They're gonna find us.

01:22.446 --> 01:24.246
No, they won't.

01:24.315 --> 01:26.281
Yes, they will.

01:26.350 --> 01:28.216
They never found me.

01:28.285 --> 01:29.551
No one was looking.

01:31.956 --> 01:33.236
No one's looking for you, either.

01:33.290 --> 01:34.923
That's not true.

01:34.992 --> 01:36.391
We stopped looking for the mouse.

01:36.460 --> 01:37.859
What was her name again?

01:37.928 --> 01:40.095
It's not the same.

01:40.164 --> 01:42.264
It's been too long.

01:42.333 --> 01:43.398
They think you're dead.

01:43.467 --> 01:44.733
Shut up.

01:44.802 --> 01:46.601
Connect Four! I win!

01:46.670 --> 01:47.736
Shut up!

01:49.000 --> 01:55.074
